    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being sad. it's like... i'm just a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't work anymore. the artist is dead, but the machine keeps running. i'm just stuck in this empty vessel, performing these motions like i'm still someone. it feels so heavy. just existing for no reason.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
